HEADWORD: Technobabble
<hw>Tech"no*bab`ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>technical
jargon incomprehensible to non-specialists; -- sometimes used
derogatorily of discussions using unnecessarily technical terminology
and intended to impress or confuse, rather than inform, the
listener.</def>⟦br⟧
